== Ibinyoro ==
Ibinyoro n'indwara y'ibasira Ikiremwa muntu,

Igafata cyane uruhu, amagufwa n'utundi duce

Nka [[Itabi|karitiraje]], ibinyoro akaba n'indwara yandura 

Hagati y'umuntu n'undi ikaba yarabayeho

Kuva kera. <ref>https://ubuzimainfo.rw/byinshi-ku-ndwara-yibinyoro-indwara-itera-kwangirika-ku-ruhu-iyo-itavuwe-kare/</ref>

== Uko indwara y'ibinyoro yandura ==
Ubusanzwe indwara y'ibinyoro n'indwara utera 

Kwangirika kuruhu iyo itavuwe kare.  

Indwara y'ibinyoro ikaba iterwa n'agakoko  

Ka [[Itabi|peretonema]] [[Itabi|peretenuwa]]. 

Indwara y ibinyoro ikaba ikunda kuboneka  

Mugihugu cyangwa mubice aho isuku arinke, 

Nanone ibinyoro bikunda kuboneka mubice  

By'amashyamba, ikaba iterwa n'isuku nkeya. 



